Package mmj.tmff

Class TMFFFormat

java.lang.Object
mmj.tmff.TMFFFormat
public class TMFFFormat extends Object
TMFFFormat holds an instantiated TMFFScheme and a format number assigned by the user.

In the future additional schemes might be assigned for Syntax Axiom level processing -- which is why TMFFFormat was created, though it seems redundant now.
